    <item>
      <title>中东紧张局势刺激避险需求，国债飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/treasuries-surge-as-middle-east-tension-stokes-demand-for-havens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东战争的预期升级刺激了对避险资产的需求，美国国债周五大幅上涨，将收益率从今年迄今的高点拉低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/treasuries-surge-as-middle-east-tension-stokes-demand-for-havens</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 12:58:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国立法者计划将非洲贸易协定 AGOA 延长至 2041 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/us-lawmakers-plan-to-extend-africa-trade-pact-agoa-through-2041</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参议员提出一项法案，将美国与约 40 个撒哈拉以南非洲国家的贸易计划延长至 2041 年，帮助它们保持进入世界最大经济体的免税准入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/us-lawmakers-plan-to-extend-africa-trade-pact-agoa-through-2041</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 12:58:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度三月份通胀因食品成本下降而降温</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/india-inflation-cools-in-march-on-decline-in-food-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于食品和燃料价格下跌，印度 3 月份零售通胀有所放缓，尽管即将到来的热浪可能会损害农作物并有可能推高价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/india-inflation-cools-in-march-on-decline-in-food-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 12:48:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗集团在利润、FICC 销售和业绩方面表现出色交易收入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-12/citigroup-beats-on-profit-ficc-sales-trading-revenue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团第一季度利润超出预期，而 FICC 销售和利润则超过预期。 41.5亿美元的交易收入超出了分析师的平均预期。索纳利·巴萨克 (Sonali Basak) 接受彭博电视台报道。]]></description>
